lastExecutor(uint256).details: Returns the msg.sender that most recently *successfuly* executed a call on the account Can't do ownerOf generically for ERC115. But we can track the last message sender to execute using the account. This may or may not be an EOA,  but MUST be the token holder and the signer

returns._0: The msg.sender that last executed or address(0) if id is unkown
